{"tid":326471,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就係「創•建前程青年招聘會｣啦!!","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T04:36:37.000Z","uid":129399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8da312fa6f1cd102eb6781305ef348e16fa2b8c","tid":326471,"uid":129399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"聽日就係搵好工既大日子！！<br />\n<br />\n7月19日(三)信義會同勞工處合辦「創&bull;建前程青年招聘會｣，不同行業既公司提供即場招聘，仲有生涯規劃服務，包括：職業興趣測試、履歷表檢視、模擬面試，仲可以即場報名參加展翅青見計劃！<br />\n<br />\n地點：基督教香港信義會啟信學校（元朗安信街10號，近元朗廣場）<br />\n時間：10:30-15:30<br />\n<br />\n如果嫌遠的話，可以考慮搭免費旅遊巴！！但記得先whatsapp登記！！<br />\n詳情請參閱海報<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何關於招聘會的查詢，可以打3956 4433搵黃小姐或者楊小姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imagemap-generator.dariodomi.de/uploads/170718_053442_0c401f24a2d4bba0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimagemap-generator.dariodomi.de%2Fuploads%2F170718_053442_0c401f24a2d4bba0.png&h=bc59a8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imagemap-generator.dariodomi.de/uploads/170718_053605_73b7be1d8f964b9v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimagemap-generator.dariodomi.de%2Fuploads%2F170718_053605_73b7be1d8f964b9v.png&h=6602a75f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}